{"tid":2244623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"之鋒：有人跟蹤我敗露後衝入地鐵站跳閘逃去","createTime":"2020-10-15T15:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T16:50:31.000Z","uid":22556,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ea5186edb68793355970743a5eb3a827bf13c5c0","tid":2244623,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T15:20:03.000Z","msg":"【跟蹤男驚到跳閘逃走】<br />\n<br />\n關於我被執法部門、左媒狗仔或各種不明勢力跟蹤滋擾，已經是司空見慣，對公眾而言亦不是新聞。不過今次拍到跟蹤男子跳閘逃跑的狼狽畫面，都是很值得跟大家分享。<br />\n<br />\n話說今晚又有一班可疑人士在我所到之處附近徘徊，其中一名男子敗露後，被與我同行的手足反過來尾隨。男子可能作賊心虛，過於驚恐，突然衝入港鐵站，更不惜違例跳閘，慌忙逃去⋯<br />\n<br />\n希望下次負責跟蹤我的人士，可以大膽些少，要有守法意識，不要丟了愛國愛港藍色陣營的架，貽笑大方 🤷🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n<br />\n．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．<br />\n💪支持我向世界展現香港人頑強抵抗的意志：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/joshuawonghk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fjoshuawonghk&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=cfe528e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/joshuawonghk</a><br />\n．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．<br />\n#存亡號召 #絕處逢生 <br />\n✍️<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/joshuawong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fjoshuawong&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=4af9cf22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/joshuawong</a><br />\n🌐<a href=\"https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=d7a39343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf</a><br />\n📷<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/joshua1013\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fjoshua1013&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=182b582f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/joshua1013</a><br />\n📧joshua@joshuawongcf.com<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/3426287337463750/?vh=e&amp;extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\